  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_5_519-582",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "519-582",
      "markText": "真正的光明绝不是永没有黑暗的时间，只是永不被黑暗所掩蔽罢了。真正的英雄绝不是永没有卑下的情操，只是永不被卑下的情操所屈服罢了。",
      "totalCount": 1428,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=519&rangeEnd=582",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=519&rangeEnd=582"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_6_720-801",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "720-801",
      "markText": "儿童期所要征服的是物质世界，青年期所要征服的是精神世界。还有最悲壮的是现在的自我和过去的自我冲突：从前费了多少心血获得的宝物，此刻要费更多的心血去反抗，以求解脱。",
      "totalCount": 1152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=720&rangeEnd=801",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=720&rangeEnd=801"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_10_16461-16540",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "16461-16540",
      "markText": "克利斯朵夫细细地想了想，原来一个人长大之后，对什么都不以为奇了，那时他神通广大，无所不知，无所不晓。于是他也装作大人，把他的好奇心藏起来，做出漠不关心的神气。",
      "totalCount": 946,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=16461&rangeEnd=16540",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=16461&rangeEnd=16540"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_5_878-925",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "878-925",
      "markText": "战士啊，当你知道世界上受苦的不止你一个时，你定会减少痛楚，而你的希望也将永远在绝望中再生了罢！",
      "totalCount": 819,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=878&rangeEnd=925",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=878&rangeEnd=925"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_18_65523-65539",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "65523-65539",
      "markText": "接着她又昏迷了……她离开了世界。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=65523&rangeEnd=65539",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=65523&rangeEnd=65539"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_10_17783-17860",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "17783-17860",
      "markText": "至于异日的征尘，虽有名城大海，虽有梦中风景，虽有爱人倩影，其刻骨铭心的程度，决比不上这些儿时的散步，或是他每天把小嘴贴在窗上嘘满了水汽所看到的园林一角……",
      "totalCount": 684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=17783&rangeEnd=17860",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=17783&rangeEnd=17860"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_10_18974-18987",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "18974-18987",
      "markText": "可是人生很快会教他屈服的。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=18974&rangeEnd=18987",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=18974&rangeEnd=18987"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_6_964-1041",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "964-1041",
      "markText": "所有的教育，所有的见闻，使一个儿童把大量的谎言与愚蠢，和人生主要的真理混在一起吞饱了，所以他若要成为一个健全的人，少年时期的第一件责任就得把宿食呕吐干净。",
      "totalCount": 660,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=964&rangeEnd=1041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=964&rangeEnd=1041"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_18_67982-68079",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "67982-68079",
      "markText": "那天晚上，安多纳德一定是和奥里维在一起：因为克利斯朵夫在奥里维眼中看见了她；而且也的确是这个突然浮现的形象使克利斯朵夫穿过客厅，向陌生的年轻的使者走过去，去接受那幸福的死者的又凄凉又温柔的敬意。",
      "totalCount": 600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=67982&rangeEnd=68079",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=67982&rangeEnd=68079"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_23_136513-136525",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "136513-136525",
      "markText": "“我是即将来到的日子。”",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=136513&rangeEnd=136525",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=136513&rangeEnd=136525"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_12_5520-5618",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "5520-5618",
      "markText": "他想到穷人怀念过去真是件可悲的事：因为他们不够资格像有钱的人一样有什么过去；他们没有一个家，世界上没有一席地可以让他们珍藏自己的回忆：他们的欢乐，他们的苦恼，他们所有的岁月，结果都在风中飘零四散。",
      "totalCount": 533,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5520&rangeEnd=5618",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5520&rangeEnd=5618"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_10_27622-27696",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "27622-27696",
      "markText": "曼希沃一边揍着孩子一边说孩子并没错，说这是侍候别人的好处，他们仗着有钱，肆无忌惮。鲁意莎一边揍着孩子一边骂丈夫野蛮，说她不答应他碰孩子，把他打伤了。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=27622&rangeEnd=27696",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=27622&rangeEnd=27696"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_10_5080-5131",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5080-5131",
      "markText": "但或许我们除了头脑、心灵、感官以外，另有一些神秘的力量，在别的力量睡着的时候乘虚而入，做了我们的主宰；",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23562203&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5080&rangeEnd=5131",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18e32440716787db18e612b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5080&rangeEnd=5131"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23562203_5_615-664",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "615-664",
      "markText": "所以在你要战胜外来的敌人之前，先得战胜你内在的敌人；你不必害怕沉沦堕落，只消你能不断地自拔与更新。",
